HEADWORD: Esteemer
<hw>Es*teem"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who esteems;
one who sets a high value on any thing.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The proudest <qex>esteemer</qex> of his own parts.</q>
<rj><qau>Locke.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ester</ent>⟦br⟧
